    <div class="news-row-right">
      <h2>Prof CM Wang - Highly Cited Researcher.</h2>
      <p>ESP is proud that Prof C.M. Wang has been included in the recent 2013 List of Highly-Cited Researchers under the Engineering Category.</p>
    <p>Click <a href="news_and_events/News/2013 news/Prof CM Wang - Highly Cited Researcher.pdf" target="new">here</a> for more details</p>
    </div>
