<div id="tab2" class="tab_content">
  <div class="news-row">
    <div class="news-row-left"><img src="news_and_events/Prospective Students/What is ESP.jpg" width="117" height="105" /></div>
    <div class="news-row-right">
      <h2>What is the Engineering Science Programme all about?</h2>
      <p>The Engineering Science Programme (ESP) exposes students to various engineering disciplines and provides a platform to integrate knowledge from the sciences and engineering through design projects, UROPs, and internships. Apart from that, the student-run ESP sub-club frequently organises social gatherings during festive seasons.</p>
      <p>
      <b>More about ESP :</b><br />
      <a href="undergraduate/degree_requirements.html">Curriculum</a> | 
      <a href="/gallery/designprojects.html">Design Projects</a> | 
